PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Health to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Commissioner of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES and the Commissioner of NUNAVUT for the transfer to their respective governments of the administration and control of the entire interest in certain public lands and chattels, namely the lands and buildings associated with the delivery of health services.
Attachments
precis:
Authority for the Minister of Health to enter into an AGREEMENT with the
Commissioner of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES and the Commissioner of NUNAVUT
for the transfer to their respective governments of the administration and
control of the entire interest in certain public lands and chattels, namely
the lands and buildings associated with the delivery of health services.
